"这一切都源于我不止一次地抱怨，提高 Quarkus "
"的启动性能变得非常困难。启动过程中，类加载的噪音非常杂乱。这意味着，每次查看启动配置文件时，你都会点击一些可疑的东西，然后意识到：\"我不知道该怎么做："

#: _posts/2026-02-24-leyden-1.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Oh well, that's just us loading a class for the first time... bummer."
msgstr "哦，好吧，这只是我们第一次装载班级......真扫兴。"

#: _posts/2026-02-24-leyden-1.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "I'm a patient person.\n"
"But you only get so many mouse clicks per day."
msgstr "我是个有耐心的人。但你每天只能点击那么几次鼠标。"

#: _posts/2026-02-24-leyden-1.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Then, one day, I took a shower, and I had this idea:"
msgstr "后来有一天，我洗了个澡，突然有了一个想法："

#: _posts/2026-02-24-leyden-1.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Isn't Project Leyden supposed to improve the class loading story, among "
"other things?"
msgstr "莱登计划不就是要改进班级装载故事和其他事情吗？"

#: _posts/2026-02-24-leyden-1.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Maybe we could use it to get rid of the class loading noise and get a "
"clearer picture of what's really going on during startup?"
msgstr "也许我们可以用它来消除类加载噪音，更清楚地了解启动过程中到底发生了什么？"

#: _posts/2026-02-24-leyden-1.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"As it turns out, this was a bit of a rabbit hole.\n"
"Project Leyden delivered results that were far better than expected, and we "
