msgstr ""
"事实证明，这是一个有点像兔子洞的地方。莱登项目取得的成果比预期的要好得多，我们最终与 Georgios 合作，将其紧密集成到了 Quarkus "
"中（你可以看到另一篇博文，对吧？）"

#: _posts/2026-02-24-leyden-1.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But today, I promised you flamegraphs. I know you're all excited about them.\n"
"Let's get to it!"
msgstr "但今天，我答应给你们火焰图。我知道你们都很兴奋让我们开始吧"

#: _posts/2026-02-24-leyden-1.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Changing the perspective"
msgstr "改变视角"

#: _posts/2026-02-24-leyden-1.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We'll explore this in more detail in a future blog post, but for now, "
"suffice it to say that Project Leyden caches classes in a loaded and linked "
"state, along with additional metadata such as method profiling information "
"and, soon, compiled code."
msgstr ""
"我们将在今后的博文中对此进行更详细的探讨，但现在只需指出，Project Leyden "
"会缓存处于加载和链接状态的类，以及其他元数据，如方法剖析信息和即将编译的代码。"

#: _posts/2026-02-24-leyden-1.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In practice, Project Leyden improves Java startup performance by shifting "
"expensive work, like class loading and linking, into a dedicated training "
"phase.\n"
"By capturing that state ahead of time, the application can skip much of the "
"redundant setup normally performed at runtime."
msgstr ""
"在实践中，Project Leyden 通过将类加载和链接等昂贵的工作转移到专门的培训阶段，提高了 Java "
"启动性能。通过提前捕获这些状态，应用程序可以跳过通常在运行时进行的大量冗余设置。"

#: _posts/2026-02-24-leyden-1.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In other words, if everything is recorded properly, class loading can be "
"almost entirely taken out of the startup path."
msgstr "换句话说，如果一切记录得当，类加载几乎可以完全从启动路径中移除。"

#: _posts/2026-02-24-leyden-1.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"And suddenly, you're in brand-new territory: the Quarkus REST application "
"you get from a simple `quarkus create app` starts in 130 milliseconds."
msgstr ""
"突然间，你进入了一个全新的领域：从一个简单的 `quarkus create app` 中获得的 Quarkus REST 应用程序只需 130 "
"毫秒即可启动。"

#: _posts/2026-02-24-leyden-1.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"That's already pretty good, right? But what's even more interesting is that "
"we were able to do much better (see you in the next blog post, remember?)."
msgstr "这已经很不错了，对吗？但更有趣的是，我们还能做得更好（下一篇博文再见，还记得吗？）"

#: _posts/2026-02-24-leyden-1.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"And this is where the perspective shifts significantly: when you start in ~ "
"100 milliseconds, every dozen milliseconds you save becomes a meaningful "
"improvement.\n"
"You can no longer afford to ignore a 5-millisecond cost."
msgstr "这就是视角发生重大转变的地方：当你从 ~ 100 毫秒开始时，每节省一打毫秒都是有意义的改进。你再也不能忽视 5 毫秒的代价。"

#: _posts/2026-02-24-leyden-1.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "I can hear someone in the room shouting:"
msgstr "我能听到房间里有人在喊叫："

#: _posts/2026-02-24-leyden-1.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Stop with the words! I want my flamegraphs!"
msgstr "别再说了我要我的火焰图"

#: _posts/2026-02-24-leyden-1.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Fine, fine."
msgstr "好吧，好吧。"

#: _posts/2026-02-24-leyden-1.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "How can we improve as an ecosystem?"
msgstr "我们如何改善生态系统？"

#: _posts/2026-02-24-leyden-1.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"One extremely important note before we begin: **we're not trying to "
