"We also found some low-hanging fruits in Quarkus itself, **we're all in the "
"same boat here**."
msgstr ""
"在开始之前，有一点非常重要： *我们在这里并不是要批评任何库或框架* 。我们在 Quarkus 中也发现了一些低垂的果实， *我们都在同一条船上* 。"

#: _posts/2026-02-24-leyden-1.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The goal of this blog post is to show how Project Leyden helped us uncover "
